ns, and comics in Africa.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aJihadxHistory. 4aAfrika. 4aDschihad. 4aIslam. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aAfrica.  aIslam.  aJihad.0 cEPUBz97831106753680 cprintz978387997727740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067527640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110675276423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110675276/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK